@cogmission You are right that those two variables are lacking mention in the doc string and that should be addressed.  There is, however, no redundancy between ```maxNewSynapseCount``` and``` maxSynapsesPerSegment```. ``` maxNewSynapseCount``` is the maximum number of synapses that can be created in one call to ```growSynapses```, while ```maxSynapsesPerSegment``` is the maximum number of synapses that can exist on a segment at any given time. 

Since you got confused about this, maybe we change the docstring for ```maxNewSynapseCount``` to read "maximum synapses that can be added during each learning step".

Let me know if that was clear.

